The '''HyperDive Cantina''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] that was part of the [[Fathoms]] resort located within [[Wildwater City]] on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Dac/Legends|Dac]]. It was owned by the undercover [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] agent [[Baydo Chasdy]] who employed a [[Kian'thar]] named [[Lliegis'Nevz]] as bartender.

